 ils\, event swag\, and raffle prizes -\ndon’t miss this meaningful and m
 emorable night!\nRain location- Irving Atrium\n\nSponsor / organizer: Dart
 mouth Dialogues\n\nAudience: Students-Undergraduate\n\nSource: Dartmouth\n
